üßµ Step 2: Create a polished installer

1. Install Inno Setup (free): https://jrsoftware.org/isinfo.php


2. Use this basic installer script (JarvisInstaller.iss):

[Setup]
AppName=Jarvis by Parthh
AppVersion=1.0
DefaultDirName={autopf}\JarvisAssistant
DefaultGroupName=Jarvis Assistant
OutputDir=output
OutputBaseFilename=JarvisInstaller
Compression=lzma
SolidCompression=yes

[Files]
Source: "dist\jarvis_full_power.exe"; DestDir: "{app}"; Flags: ignoreversion
Source: "stark_icon.ico"; DestDir: "{app}"; Flags: ignoreversion

[Icons]
Name: "{group}\Jarvis"; Filename: "{app}\jarvis_full_power.exe"; IconFilename: "{app}\stark_icon.ico"

[Run]
Filename: "{app}\jarvis_full_power.exe"; Description: "Launch Jarvis"; Flags: nowait postinstall skipifsilent


